    "lyrics": {
      "text": "Lord, when Thou didst as-cend up-on the Cross, Thou didst ut-ter-ly o-blit-er-ate__ our an-ces-tral curse. And go-ing down in-to Ha-des, Thou didst set free those in fet-ters from all ag-es past, grant-ing un-to the race of man in-cor-rup-tion for ev-er; hence, for this cause with hymns do we glo-ri--fy Thy life-cre-at--ing and sav-ing Ris-ing from the dead."
    }
